Implement start_workflow handler per ADR-012:
- Extract ActorRef<OrchestratorMsg> from Extension layer
- Call actor via call_t! with timeout
- Return StartWorkflowResponse on success
- Map OrchestratorMsg::StartWorkflow to API response

```rust
pub async fn start_workflow(
    Extension(master): Extension<ActorRef<OrchestratorMsg>>,
    Json(payload): Json<StartWorkflowRequest>,
) -> Result<Json<StartWorkflowResponse>, StatusCode> {
    let reply = master.call_t(OrchestratorMsg::StartWorkflow {
        name: payload.workflow_name.clone(),
        input: payload.input.clone(),
        reply: RpcReplyPort::new(),
    }, Duration::from_secs(5)).await.map_err(|_| StatusCode::INTERNAL_SERVER_ERROR)?;
    // ... map response
}
```

